<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-20815] exchange.getVariable does not get Global variables in custom processor</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-20815</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This one does not work in custom processor:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Object&lt;/span&gt; val1 = exchange.getVariable(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;global:testVar&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);&#160;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;This one works fine:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Object&lt;/span&gt; val2 = exchange.getContext().getVariable(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;testVar&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);&#160;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
